@startuml
[*] --> Idle
Idle --> ChangeHour : press button
ChangeHour --> ChangeMinutes : press button
ChangeMinutes --> AlarmHour : press button
AlarmHour --> AlarmMinutes : press button
AlarmMinutes --> AdjustingTime : increase value
AdjustingTime --> Idle : decrease value
Idle --> AlarmOn : turn on alarm
AlarmOn --> AlarmOff : turn off alarm
AlarmOff --> AlarmTriggered : set alarm time matches current time
AlarmTriggered --> AlarmStopped : stop alarm by pressing button
AlarmStopped --> Idle : press button to return to idle state
Idle --> LightOn : press button to turn on light
LightOn --> LightOff : release button to turn off light
@enduml
